Package: textminingKCIRISS
Title: Text Mining Korean Academic Data using R
Version: 1.1.0
Date: 2025-01-02
Authors@R:
    person("Yeondong", "Yang", , "rubato103@dodaseo.cc", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: An integrated pipeline for morphological analysis, N-gram extraction,
    and topic modeling of Korean academic paper data from KCI (Korea Citation Index)
    and RISS (Research Information Sharing Service). Provides automated workflow
    with Kiwipiepy morphological analyzer, compound noun dictionary management,
    and STM (Structural Topic Model) for temporal analysis.
License: file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/rubato103/textmining_KCI_RISS
